- Bye, Mom!

01:32:21.244 --> 01:32:22.786
Just a quick one.

01:32:23.872 --> 01:32:25.206
And...

01:32:25.290 --> 01:32:28.209
Not over any oceans, Scott.

01:32:28.293 --> 01:32:31.462
- Bye, Mom! Bye!
- Scott.

01:32:32.214 --> 01:32:34.423
Scott!

01:32:34.674 --> 01:32:36.592
Santa!

